```xml
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    package="com.madhub.facebookaccountactiv">

    <!-- Required to define the app's permissions for network access -->
    <!-- Achieves uninterrupted communication with social media platforms, enhancing user engagement -->
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
    
    <!-- Required for accessing device storage -->
    <!-- Improves efficiency by enabling management of local data, such as schedules and logs -->
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />

    <!-- Define the application -->
    <application
        android:allowBackup="true"
        android:icon="@mipmap/ic_launcher"
        android:label="@string/app_name"
        android:roundIcon="@mipmap/ic_launcher_round"
        android:supportsRtl="true"
        android:theme="@style/Theme.AppCompat.Light.NoActionBar">
        
        <!-- MainActivity declaration -->
        <!-- Responsible for initiating user interactions, enhancing user experience from the start -->
        <activity android:name=".MainActivity">
            <intent-filter>
                <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
                <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
            </intent-filter>
        </activity>
        
        <!-- AutomationService declaration -->
        <!-- Enables 24/7 automated operations, boosting productivity and ensuring consistent activity management -->
        <service
            android:name=".AutomationService"
            android:enabled="true"
            android:exported="false" />
        
    </application>

</manifest>
```

### Explanation of Key Elements:
- **Permissions**: The `INTERNET` permission is crucial for ensuring real-time communication with social media platforms, which enhances user engagement and connectivity. The storage permissions allow efficient management of data, such as being able to store logs and configuration files locally, leading to a more streamlined user experience. 
- **MainActivity**: This component serves as the entry point of the application, significantly improving user experience and engagement from the moment the app is launched.
- **AutomationService**: This service facilitates continual background operations, promoting operational efficiency and ensuring that tasks are carried out consistently. This capability directly correlates with increased productivity and management efficiency for users of the MadHub tool. 

The provided configuration ensures that the application is set up for optimal performance while emphasizing its compliance with best practices in Android development.
